t;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Liver Tonic</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:  normal"><u><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"><span style="text-decoration:none"><br type="_moz" />  </span></span></u></i></b></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:  normal"><u><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Quy cách đóng gói</span></u></i></b><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;"> : H&ocirc;̣p 100 vi&ecirc;n, 365 vi&ecirc;n.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:  normal"><u><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Thành ph&acirc;̀n c&acirc;́u tạo</span></u></i></b><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">: </span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Taurine 150mg, psylium 100mg, lecithin 20mg, silybum marianum seed 7g, Schisandra chinensis fruit 160mg, taraxacum officinale root 200mg.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:  normal"><u><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Thành ph&acirc;̀n khác</span></u></i></b><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">: Vừa đủ 1 vi&ecirc;n.</span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:  normal"><u><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">C&ocirc;ng dụng</span></u></i></b><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">: </span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">-<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">H&ocirc;̃ trợ dinh dưỡng quan trọng cho chức năng gan khỏe mạnh.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">-<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Ngăn ngừa t&ocirc;̉n hại đ&ocirc;́i với các t&ecirc;́ bào gan, h&ocirc;̃ trợ đi&ecirc;̀u trị gan nhi&ecirc;̃m mỡ, suy gan do rượu, xơ gan, vi&ecirc;m gan B và vi&ecirc;m gan si&ecirc;u vi C, men gan tăng cao. Cải thi&ecirc;̣n tri&ecirc;̣u chứng ăn khó ti&ecirc;u do gan. Ch&ocirc;́ng dị ứng, n&ocirc;̉i m&ecirc;̀ đay do gan.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">-<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Đi&ecirc;̀u trị t&acirc;̣n g&ocirc;́c mụn bọc và mụn trứng cá.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left:6.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:  normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal"><u><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Cơ ch&ecirc;́ tác dụng</span></u></i></b><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">: </span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">-<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Tác dụng bảo v&ecirc;̣ gan, giải đ&ocirc;̣c cho gan, bảo v&ecirc;̣ nhu m&ocirc; gan và hi&ecirc;̣u quả t&ocirc;́t với các trường hợp h&ocirc;̃ trợ đi&ecirc;̀u trị.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">-<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Vi&ecirc;m gan c&acirc;́p do rượu, xơ gan, vi&ecirc;m gan B và vi&ecirc;m gan si&ecirc;u vi C.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">-<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Các thu&ocirc;́c có đ&ocirc;̣c tính với gan, các trường hợp chức năng thải đ&ocirc;̣c của gan kém.</span></p>  <p style="margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;  tab-stops:list 24.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;VnTime&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;  mso-fareast-font-family:VnTime;mso-bidi-font-family:VnTime"><span 